# vim:ft=conf

### General Options:
--default-search "ytsearch"
--mark-watched
--live-from-start
--color 'stderr:always'

### Download Options:
# --downloader "dash,m3u8:aria2c"
--concurrent-fragments 4

### Filesystem Options:
